doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    meta(name='mobile-web-app-capable', content='yes')
    title Shower Presentation Engine
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='build/build.css')

  body
    article.deck
      section.title.image(style='background-image: url(images/cover.jpg); background-size: cover', data-title='')
        h1 Shower Presentation Engine
        p As emulated by #[a(href='http://markdalgleish.com/projects/bespoke.js') Bespoke.js]

      section
        h2 Shower Key Features
        ol
          li Built on HTML, CSS and vanilla JavaScript
          li All modern browsers are supported
          li Slide themes are separated from engine
          li Fully keyboard accessible
          li Printable to PDF
        p.note Shower ['ʃəuə] noun. A person or thing that shows.

      section
        h2 Plain Text on Your Slides
        p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur #[a(href='#4') adipisicing] elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, #[em quis nostrud] exercitation ullamco laboris #[strong nisi ut aliquip] ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure #[em dolor] in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum #[strong dolore] eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in #[code &lt;culpa&gt;] qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.

      section
        h2 All Kinds of Lists
        ol
          li Simple lists are marked with bullets
          li Ordered lists begin with a number
          li
            |You can even nest lists one inside another
            ul
              li Or mix their types
              li But do not go too far
              li Otherwise audience will be bored
          li Look, seven rows exactly!

      section
        h2 Serious Citations
        figure.quote
