            td Jean
            td Shorts
            td Biodiesel
          tr
            th Terry
            td Richardson
            td Swag
            td Blog
        p It's good to have information organized.

      section.image(style='background-image: url(images/picture.jpg); background-size: cover')
        h2 Pictures
      
      section.shout
        h2 You can even shout this way

      section
        h2 Inner Navigation
        ol
          li.build Lets you reveal list items one by one
          li.build To keep some key points
          li.build In secret from audience
          li.build But it will work only once
          li.build Nobody wants to see the same joke twice 

